      <c01 level="series" id="fd3542f0-c9e8-11e5-a6aa-18cf5eb0caa7">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Administrative</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Administrative series contains files of the Executive Director, the Board of Trustees, administrative committees, by-laws, budgets, financial reports and statements, strategic planning documentation; materials related to the Michigan Theater restoration: surveys, reports, and plans; materials related to membership campaigns, volunteer recruitment, and staff newsletters. Also included articles and interview notes taken by Russell Collins on the subject of history of Ann Arbor's three theater venues --Hill's Opera House, the Whitney Theater, and Michigan Theater; programs and newspaper advertisements of performances at the Ann Arbor theaters; and Collins' article on the subject of history of American musical theater.</p>
        </scopecontent>
